* Requirements (Debian package name given in brackets)
  - GCC               (gcc, g++)
  - GNU Bison         (bison)
  - GNU Flex          (flex)
  - Alsa audio        (libasound2, libasound2-dev)
  - Expat             (libexpat1, libexpat1-dev)
  - help2man          (help2man)
  - devscripts package and its dependencies in order to build Debian packages  (devscripts)
 
* Build
  - Compile:
    make
  - This will install executables in $(bindir) (see Makefile)
  - Make debian packages:
    make debian-packages
   - This will generate the following deb packages:
       ../cotovia_version-name_arch.deb
       ../cotovia-ecess-m1_version-name_arch.deb
       ../data/cotovia-lang-gl_version-name_all.deb
       ../data/cotovia-lang-es_version-name_all.deb
       ../data/cotovia-voice-iago_version-name_all.deb

